==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Open wide the door of convenience.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà kāi fāng biàn zhī mén

===Idiom===
'''[[大]][[開]][[方便之門]]'''

# Do someone a big favor.

===Alternate forms===
[[大开方便之门]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

